data.description: Welcome home! This beautiful home in Mackintosh on the lake is priced to sell! With 4 bedrooms, two bathrooms, on the second floor, and a finished bonus room with closet, full bathroom and floored attic space on the third floor, this home has plenty to offer! Fireplace in the very spacious primary bedroom creates a great ambiance for relaxing. Fenced in back yard with back porch and patio, perfect for entertaining.  Mackintosh on the lake offers miles of sidewalks, pool, basketball and tennis courts, clubhouse, fitness center and many more amenities. All of this less than 5 minutes from I-40!
